          "3.28 Tattvavit  tu etc.   On the other hand, the  knower of  the real  nature of divisions of the Strands and of their  actions,  sets himself  free by viewing  'The Prakrti acts;  what  comes to men ?'\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n The ignorant men have been described as being attached to action (above III,  26).  That  attachment [of theirs,  the Lord]  demonstrates :",
