    "abhinav": {
      "author": "Sri Abhinav Gupta",
      "et":
          "3.3 Loke etc.  In the world, this twofold path is well known.  Knowledge is important for men of reflection and action for men of Yoga.  But that path has been declared by Me to be only one.  For, the Consciousness consists predominantly of knowledg and action.  This is the idea here. \t\t\t\t\t\n For this [the Lord continues] -",
      "sc":
          "।।3.3।।श्रीभगवांस्तूत्तरं ददाति लोकेऽस्मिन् इति।  लोके एषा द्वयी गतिः प्रसिद्धा  सांख्यानां ज्ञानं प्रधानम् योगिनां च कर्मेति।  मया तु सा एकैव निष्ठा उक्ता ज्ञानक्रियामयत्वात् संवित्तत्त्वस्येति भावः।"
    },
